default4.default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultICAEW is a professional membership organisation, supporting over 14
default2
default,000 chartered accountants around 
defaultthe world. Through our technical knowledge, skills and expertise, we provide insight and leadership to the global accountancy and finance profession.
default&#xa0;
default5.default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultOur members provide financial knowledge and guidance based on the highest professional, technical and eth
defaultical standards. We develop and support individuals, organisations and communities to help them achieve long-term, sustainable economic value.
default&#xa0;
default6.default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultThe Tax Faculty is the voice of tax within ICAEW and is a leading authority on taxation. Internationally recognis
defaulted as a source of expertise, the faculty is responsible for submissions to tax authorities on behalf of ICAEW as a whole. It also provides a range of tax services, including 
defaultTAXline
default, a monthly journal sent to more than 8,000 members, a weekly newswire and 
defaulta referral scheme.
